Version:        1.1.2
Release:        alt1
Summary:        Sphinx API for Web Apps
License:        BSD
Group:          Development/Python3
BuildArch:      noarch
URL:            http://sphinx-doc.org/

# https://github.com/sphinx-doc/sphinxcontrib-websupport.git
